.TH USENUPAS 8
.SH NAME
usenupas \- test new upas
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B usenupas
.SH DESCRIPTION
.I Usenupas
allows one to test the new upas
before it becomes the default,
given an appropriate installation
of
.IR Nupas .
To enable parallel installation of
the new and old versions, modify
.B /sys/src/cmd/upas/mkupas
to install in
.B /$\f2objtype\f5/bin/nupas
.PP
Typically 
.I usenupas
should be sourced from
.B /usr/\f2user\f5/lib/profile
after one's mailbox has been converted
to
.IR mdir (6)
format.
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.IR mdir (6),
.IR pop3 (8),
.IR splitmbox (8)
.SH BUGS
This is for testing only and is depricated.
.PP
It's imperative that one close all IMAP
clients using the old upas system.
